Have you ever wanted higher quality images on the Roblox website, well now you can!

This free extension upscales images on the Roblox website to be much higher quality, such as:
- Game Icons
- Player Icons
- Group Icons
- Player Avatar
- Catalog Items
- Game Thumbnails
- Today's Picks Thumbnails

If you've encountered bugs or have feedback, send me a message on X (@RobTosPro) or my contact email below.
